results.name: Moon Knight
results.description: On Reveal: Discard a card from each player's hand.

results.name: Morbius
results.description: Ongoing: +2 Power for each time you discarded a card this game.

results.name: Morph
results.description: On Reveal: Become a copy of a random card in your opponent's hand.

results.name: Multiple Man
results.description: When this moves, add a copy to the old location.

results.name: Mysterio
results.description: As you play this, play Illusions to other locations. Disguise this as an Illusion until the game ends.

results.name: Mystique
results.description: On Reveal: If the last card you played has an Ongoing ability, this card gains it.

results.name: Nakia
results.description: On Reveal: Give the 2 leftmost cards in your hand +2 Power.

results.name: Namor
results.description: Ongoing: +5 Power if this is your only card here.

results.name: Negasonic Teenage Warhead
results.description: After ANY card is played here, destroy this card AND that card.

results.name: Nick Fury
results.description: On Reveal: Add 3 random 6-Cost cards to your hand.

results.name: Nightcrawler
results.description: You can move this once.

results.name: Nimrod
results.description: When this is destroyed, add a copy to each other location.

results.name: Nova
results.description: When this is destroyed, give your cards +1 Power.

results.name: Odin
results.description: On Reveal: Activate the On Reveal abilities of your other cards at this location.

results.name: Okoye
results.description: On Reveal: Give every card in your deck +1 Power.

results.name: Omega Red
results.description: Ongoing: If you're ahead by 10 Power here, +4 Power to other locations.

results.name: Onslaught
results.description: Ongoing: Double your other Ongoing effects at this location.

results.name: Orka
results.description: Ongoing: +5 Power if this is your only card here.

results.name: Patriot
results.description: Ongoing: Your cards with no abilities have +2 Power.

results.name: Polaris
results.description: On Reveal: Move an opposing 1 or 2-Cost card to this location.

results.name: Professor X
results.description: Ongoing: Lock down this location. (Cards can't be added, removed, etc.)

results.name: Psylocke
results.description: On Reveal: Next turn, you get +1 Energy.

results.name: Punisher
results.description: Ongoing: +1 Power for each opposing card at this location.

results.name: Quake
results.description: On Reveal: If this is at the middle location, swap the positions of each location.
